<h1>Ably Channel History Example</h1>

<p>In this example, we demonstrate how to easily retrieve continuous message history on a channel i.e. all messages up until the point the channel was attached. See <a href="https://www.ably.io/documentation/realtime/history">our Realtime continuous history documentation</a> for more details.

<div class="row">
  <input id="publish" type="submit" value="Publish a message">
</div>

<div class="row">
  <input id="history" type="submit" value="Attach channel & get untilAttach history">
</div>

<ul class="row" id="message-status"></ul>
